high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the white table to the left of the dishwasher.
Pick up the head of lettuce in the front, middle of the table.
Turn to your left and walk to the sink.
Place the head of lettuce in the sink, next to the edge closest to the microwave.
Turn to your left and walk to the white table with two heads of lettuce on it.
Pick up the head of lettuce between the tomato and the butter knife.
Turn to your right and walk back to the sink.
Place the head of lettuce in the sink, to the right of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put two heads of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the white table with the lettuce on it.
Pick the lettuce up from the table.
Turn around and cross the room to stand facing the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the white table with the tomato on it.
Pick the lettuce on the right up from the table.
Turn and cross the room to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two heads of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Move forward but move to your left so you are facing the white kitchen table
Pick up the lettuce off of the table
Turn around and then walk to your right until you are facing the sink
Place the lettuce in to the sink
Turn around and then turn to face the right hand side kitchen table
Pick up the lettuce off of the table
Turn back to your right so you are facing the sink again
Place this lettuce in to the sink too
anns.task_desc: Put 2 lettuce heads in the sink
